
React-speak

Props is how information is passed from parent to child. Attributes in HTML

State === memory, how components remember things/a component's conscious

Immutability - method of working with data, where you keep the original clean, working of a copy of the original. Easier to detect changes

Functional component - only contains a render method, no state. 

Javascript methods

.slice(i) 
	-make a shallow copy of array
	-create new array, beginning at i. 